According to the HFPC of Chongqing, Kaizhou district reported one human H7N9 AIV case after the reconfirmation from Chongqing CDC on 4 Jun 2017. The 37-year-old female, resident of Kaizhou district, remained in hospital for treatment.

So far, Chongqing has reported 8 human H7N9 AIV cases.

