[4] Sichuan
Date: 6 Jun 2017
Source: FIC (Flu Information Centre/Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news_detail?action=ql&uid=MjI0OA&pd=YXRsbXBw&newsId=19475


According to the government of Renshou county, Zhangjia town of Renshou county of Meishan city reported one human H7N9 AIV case on 25 May 2017. This is the 1st human H7N9 AIV case reported in Meishan city.

The 67-year-old male, resident of Zhangjia town of Renshou county, was in serious condition and remained in Renshou county people's hospital for treatment and quarantine.

